        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mince is cooking, dice your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Cut your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>in half</p>",
